Package info.oais.infomodel.interfaces

Interface PackagingInformation

All Superinterfaces:
InformationObject, RepresentationInformation
public interface PackagingInformation extends InformationObject, RepresentationInformation
The information that describes how the components of an Information Package are logically or physically bound together and how to identify and extract the components. It is a type of Information Object. [OAIS]

NOTE: Added "extends RepInfo" so we can use RepInfo APIs.
